  "local_port": 45018,
  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "What are the best location to invest in Ahmedabad?",
  "response": "Investing in real estate in Ahmedabad can be a lucrative decision given the city's rapid development and economic growth. As of the most recent data, here are some of the best locations to consider for real estate investment in Ahmedabad:\n\n1. **SG Highway (Sarkhej-Gandhinagar Highway):**\n   - Well-connected and rapidly developing, SG Highway is a prime location with multiple commercial developments and residential projects. It offers easy access to key parts of the city and is a preferred location for professionals working in nearby IT hubs.\n\n2. **Bopal and South Bopal:**\n   - These are popular residential areas with developed infrastructure, including schools, hospitals, and shopping centers. The area has seen significant growth and offers a mix of affordable and premium housing options.\n\n3. **Prahlad Nagar:**\n   - Known for its corporate offices and high-end residential projects, Prahlad Nagar is an upscale area with excellent amenities. It is a preferred choice for professionals and families seeking a modern lifestyle.\n\n4. **Thaltej:**\n   - Located close to SG Highway, Thaltej offers a mix of residential and commercial properties. It is well-connected and boasts good infrastructure and amenities.\n\n5. **Vastrapur:**\n   - Known for its lake and park, Vastrapur is a well-established residential area. It offers high-quality living with good schools, hospitals, and shopping facilities nearby.\n\n6. **Gota:**\n   - Gota is a rapidly developing area with several new residential projects. It has good connectivity to the city and is becoming increasingly popular among homebuyers and investors.\n\n7. **New Ranip:**\n   - Emerging as a promising location for investment, New Ranip offers affordable housing options with developing infrastructure. It is gaining popularity due to its proximity to the Ahmedabad Railway Station and other key areas.\n\n8. **Motera:**\n   - Known for the Narendra Modi Stadium, Motera is witnessing growth in both residential and commercial real estate. Its connectivity and infrastructure make it an attractive investment destination.\n\n9. **Chandkheda:**\n   - Close to industrial and commercial zones, Chandkheda is popular among professionals working in these sectors. It offers affordable and mid-range housing options.\n\nBefore investing, it's crucial to consider factors such as budget, long-term plans, infrastructure developments, and market trends. Consulting with local real estate experts or agents can also provide valuable insights specific to your investment goals.",
